  "root_text": {
    "iti32:0.1": "Itivuttaka 32 ",
    "iti32:0.2": "Dukanipāta ",
    "iti32:0.3": "Paṭhamavagga ",
    "iti32:0.4": "Paṭhamasīlasutta ",
    "iti32:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti32:2.1": "“Dvīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato puggalo yathābhataṁ nikkhitto evaṁ niraye. ",
    "iti32:2.2": "Katamehi dvīhi? ",
    "iti32:2.3": "Pāpakena ca sīlena, pāpikāya ca diṭṭhiyā. ",
    "iti32:2.4": "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dvīhi dhammehi samannāgato puggalo yathābhataṁ nikkhitto evaṁ niraye”ti. ",
    "iti32:2.5": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti32:2.6": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti32:3.1": "“Pāpakena ca sīlena, ",
    "iti32:3.2": "pāpikāya ca diṭṭhiyā; ",
    "iti32:3.3": "Etehi dvīhi dhammehi, ",
    "iti32:3.4": "yo samannāgato naro; ",
    "iti32:3.5": "Kāyassa bhedā duppañño, ",
    "iti32:3.6": "nirayaṁ sopapajjatī”ti. ",
    "iti32:4.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti32:4.2": "Pañcamaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti32:0.1": "So It Was Said 32 ",
    "iti32:0.2": "The Book of the Twos ",
    "iti32:0.3": "Chapter One ",
    "iti32:0.4": "Ethics (1st) ",
    "iti32:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti32:2.1": "“Mendicants, an individual with two qualities is placed in hell as if delivered there. ",
    "iti32:2.2": "What two? ",
    "iti32:2.3": "Bad conduct and bad view. ",
    "iti32:2.4": "A individual with these two qualities is placed in hell as if delivered there.” ",
    "iti32:2.5": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti32:2.6": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti32:3.1": "“If a person possesses ",
    "iti32:3.2": "these two qualities—",
    "iti32:3.3": "bad conduct ",
    "iti32:3.4": "and bad views—",
    "iti32:3.5": "when their body breaks up, that witless person ",
    "iti32:3.6": "is reborn in hell.” ",
    "iti32:4.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
